{"tid":332444,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人真係好有教養","createTime":"2017-07-23T04:10:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-30T11:22:01.000Z","uid":79860,"like":14,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"763386d82bde6dfb9c6b750a323057a496630d5d","tid":332444,"uid":79860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T04:10:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌你老母 有條撚！</span><br />\n<br />\n無禮貌 貪小便宜 又厚面皮 <br />\n特別係啲上年紀既吖嬸同唔識教小朋友既父母<br />\n<br />\n講返背景先 以下既情況係之前做part time返一間會派試食既鋪頭每日遇到既事<br />\n<br />\n1. 貪小便宜厚面皮既吖嬸<br />\n每星期見佢黎食幾次 每次黎問同一樣既問題扮新客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  一路問一路食 仲要以為我認你唔到 但每次食完都唔會買 食完就走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2.唔識教小朋友既家長<br />\n有時有啲小朋友見到有試食就好似失控咁沖過黎食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  跟住一食就食左我一半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   老豆老母見到覺得唔好意思就叫個小朋友停 但好多都唔撚識聽指令<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  直接拉走個小朋友啦屌 唔好得把口好冇?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.貪小便宜既人<br />\n無試食嘅時侯 過黎睇都唔會睇下#<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#<br />\n跟住當有試食既時候 就會有一班好似餓狗咁嘅人過黎搶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但睇清楚當中每一個人既面孔 全部都係啲食慣食熟嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  次次食完之後比同一樣滿足既表情就走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  屌！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 下面係示意圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/23/115917_957132c49e62759de4ad5330e0d3a1ff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F23%2F115917_957132c49e62759de4ad5330e0d3a1ff.jpg&h=06c9a5c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家唔係唔比你食 但試食唔係任食呀 屌你老母 比d教養啦香港人！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好彩間唔中都會遇到一啲有教養有禮貌既人 但只有極之少數 自己身為香港人都覺得悲哀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bf98589cca85a721c9bc824f615f7a5810af855","tid":332444,"uid":79860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T04:39:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌你老母 有條撚！</span><br />\n<br />\n無禮貌 貪小便宜 又厚面皮 <br />\n特別係啲上年紀既吖嬸同唔識教小朋友既父母<br />\n<br />\n講返背景先 以下既情況係之前做part time返一間會派試食既鋪頭每日遇到既事<br />\n<br />\n1. 貪小便宜厚面皮既吖嬸<br />\n每星期見佢黎食幾次 每次黎問同一樣既問題扮新客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  一路問一路食 仲要以為我認你唔到 但每次食完都唔會買 食完就走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2.唔識教小朋友既家長<br />\n有時有啲小朋友見到有試食就好似失控咁沖過黎食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  跟住一食就食左我一半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   老豆老母見到覺得唔好意思就叫個小朋友停 但好多都唔撚識聽指令<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  直接拉走個小朋友啦屌 唔好得把口好冇?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.貪小便宜既人<br />\n無試食嘅時侯 過黎睇都唔會睇下#<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#<br />\n跟住當有試食既時候 就會有一班好似餓狗咁嘅人過黎搶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但睇清楚當中每一個人既面孔 全部都係啲食慣食熟嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  次次食完之後比同一樣滿足既表情就走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  屌！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 下面係示意圖<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.downloadfeast.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/dog-girl-