ass=\"hkgmoji\" />  屌！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 下面係示意圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/23/115917_957132c49e62759de4ad5330e0d3a1ff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F23%2F115917_957132c49e62759de4ad5330e0d3a1ff.jpg&h=06c9a5c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家唔係唔比你食 但試食唔係任食呀 屌你老母 比d教養啦香港人！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好彩間唔中都會遇到一啲有教養有禮貌既人 但只有極之少數 自己身為香港人都覺得悲哀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n試完一輪唔買先仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba17afccede840f2c75aef8def8b8a68cba23956","tid":332444,"uid":79860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T11:22:01.000Z","msg":"頭先忍唔住鬧左個新移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想知再講<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}